        What to Expect When Selling in Annerley
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Annerley is an inner-south suburb in the process of repricing. Buyers who have been pushed out of Dutton Park and Fairfield are arriving here and finding genuine value in a suburb that is closer to the city than its price tag has historically suggested.
      </p>
